Install font with homebrew:
	brew tap homebrew/cask-fonts
	brew install --cask font-hack-nerd-font

	https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts

iTerm2 -> Preferences -> Profiles -> Text -> Font
	Select "Hack Nerd Font"

Add the following to .zshrc
	fpath=(/my/path/to/zsh/prompt $fpath)
	autoload -Uz name_of_the_prompt_file; name_of_the_prompt_file

Example:
	fpath=(~/zsh_config $fpath)
	autoload -Uz zshrc_prompt_file; zshrc_prompt_file
